          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "A valid buffer containing the histogram results for the source image. This filter will use these histogram results to generate the cumulative histogram for equalizing the image.  The histogram results per channel are stored together. The number of channels for which histogram results are stored is determined by the number of channels in the image. If the ",
